::/128          - unspecified
::/0            - default unicast
::1/128         - loopback
fe80::/10       - link local
fc00::/7        - unique local
::ffff:0:0/96   - IPv4 mapped IPv6
::ffff:0:0:0/96 - Stateless IP/ICMP Translation
64:ff9b::/96    - WellKnown prefix
2002::/16       - 6to4


Use Hex to write cool IPv6 addresses:

  2001:0DB8:0000:CD30:0123:4567:89AB:CDEF
  BAD:BAD:BAD
  DEAD:BEEF:DEAD:BEEF:DEAD:BEEF:DEAD:BEEF
  2001:0DB8:0000:CD30:DEAD:BEEF:DEAD:BEEF
  BAD:F00
